{******************************************************************************

External symbol tables

Maps the external symbols of each bound module to routine numbers
for the interpreter: the table index is the routine number within
the module. Symbols can far exceed a source line (an event record
digest passes 1400 characters), and no two symbols share even a
40 character prefix, so the entries hold an 80 character prefix
and the lookup matches on the prefix.

Generated by tools/extgen/gen.py; do not edit by hand. The
services order is frozen (the execservices routine numbers
depend on it); other modules are in declaration order.

******************************************************************************}

